---
title: Jalapeño Popper Pork Burgers with Sweet Potato Rounds
description: This classic appetizer just got upgraded to the burger section of the menu! Cream cheese, cheddar cheese and jalapeños sit atop a juicy pork burger, while sweet potato rounds complete this lip-smacking explosion of flavour!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burgers-de-porc-aux-jalapenos-4c79db68.jpg
